  "body": "# AIOTs Expanded\nA fabric add-on mod for [Basic AIOTs](https://modrinth.com/mod/basic-aiots) that aims to greatly expand compatibility with other mods\n\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/aiots-expanded-fabric\"><img src=\"http://cf.way2muchnoise.eu/full_632976_downloads.svg\"></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/aiotsexpanded\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/dynamic/json?color=5da545&label=%E2%80%8B&labelColor=cecece&query=downloads&suffix=%20downloads&url=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.modrinth.com%2Fapi%2Fv1%2Fmod%2Faiotsexpanded&logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,\"></a>\n\nCurrently supported mods include:\n- [Mythic Metals](https://modrinth.com/mod/mythicmetals)\n- [BetterEnd](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/betterend)\n- [BetterNether](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/betternether)\n- [Advanced Netherite](https://modrinth.com/mod/advanced-netherite)\n- [Warden Loot](https://modrinth.com/mod/wardenloot)\n\nWith many more planned\n\n<img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/597633988802117642/992897298415759480/aiots.png\" width=\"450\"/>\n \nCredits:\n\n[Luligabi12](https://www.curseforge.com/members/luligabi12/projects) for template textures/mod icon\n\nAll of the respective mod authors for the original tool-set textures\n\n<sub>Note: I am not affiliated with the author of the Basic AIOTs mod</sub>",
